msgid "Verify Your Email"
msgstr "Bestätige deine E-Mail"

#: templates/account/verified_email_required_crush.html:20
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    Before you can continue, we need to verify your email address.\n"
"                    Please check your inbox for a verification link from Crush.lu.\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    Bevor du fortfahren kannst, müssen wir deine E-Mail-Adresse bestätigen.\n"
"                    Bitte sieh in deinem Posteingang nach einem Bestätigungslink von Crush.lu.\n"
"                "

#: templates/account/verified_email_required_crush.html:26
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    Don't see the email? Check your spam folder or request a new link below.\n"
"                    The email is sent from <strong>noreply@crush.lu</strong>.\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    Du siehst die E-Mail nicht? Sieh in deinem Spam-Ordner nach oder fordere unten einen neuen Link an.\n"
"                    Die E-Mail wird von <strong>noreply@crush.lu</strong> versendet.\n"
"                "

