#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:4
msgid "Become a Crush Coach - Help Singles Connect in Luxembourg"
msgstr "Werde Crush Coach - Hilf Singles in Luxemburg sich zu vernetzen"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:6
msgid "Become a Crush Coach - Join Our Team"
msgstr "Werde Crush Coach - Tritt unserem Team bei"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:7
msgid ""
"Help Luxembourg singles find meaningful connections. Become a Crush Coach — "
"host events, verify members in person, and make a real difference. Flexible "
"and rewarding."
msgstr ""
"Hilf Singles in Luxemburg, echte Verbindungen zu finden. Werde Crush Coach —"
" organisiere Events, verifiziere Mitglieder persönlich und bewirke etwas. "
"Flexibel und erfüllend."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:9
msgid ""
"Join the Crush.lu coaching team. Host events, verify members in person, "
"facilitate connections, and help singles in Luxembourg meet face-to-face. "
"Flexible hours, full training provided."
msgstr ""
"Werde Teil des Crush.lu-Coaching-Teams. Organisiere Events, verifiziere "
"Mitglieder persönlich, fördere Verbindungen und hilf Singles in Luxemburg, "
"sich persönlich zu treffen. Flexible Zeiten, vollständige Einarbeitung."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:10
msgid ""
"crush coach, volunteer dating coach, luxembourg singles, coach recruitment, "
"crush.lu team, dating event host"
msgstr ""
"crush coach, ehrenamtlicher dating coach, luxemburg singles, coach "
"rekrutierung, crush.lu team, dating event gastgeber"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:30
#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:76
msgid "Become a Crush Coach"
msgstr "Werde Crush Coach"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:43
msgid ""
"Help Luxembourg singles find meaningful connections. Host events, verify "
"members in person at check-in, and facilitate post-event connections."
msgstr ""
"Hilf Singles in Luxemburg, echte Verbindungen zu finden. Organisiere Events,"
" verifiziere Mitglieder persönlich beim Check-in und fördere Verbindungen "
"nach dem Event."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:77
msgid ""
"Help Luxembourg singles find meaningful connections. Guide them from first "
"profile to first date and make a real difference in people's lives."
msgstr ""
"Hilf Luxemburger Singles, bedeutungsvolle Verbindungen zu finden. Begleite "
"sie vom ersten Profil bis zum ersten Date und mache einen echten Unterschied"
" im Leben anderer."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:79
msgid "Contact Us"
msgstr "Kontaktiere uns"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:80
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "Mehr erfahren"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:88
msgid "In Person"
msgstr "Persönlich"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:89
msgid "Verify at Events"
msgstr "Bei Events verifizieren"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:93
msgid "3 Languages"
msgstr "3 Sprachen"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:94
msgid "EN / DE / FR"
msgstr "EN / DE / FR"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:98
msgid "Flexible Hours"
msgstr "Flexible Zeiten"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:99
msgid "Work on Your Schedule"
msgstr "Arbeite nach deinem Zeitplan"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:106
msgid "Why Become a Coach?"
msgstr "Warum Coach werden?"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:107
msgid ""
"Coaching is more than a role — it's a chance to shape Luxembourg's dating "
"culture."
msgstr ""
"Coaching ist mehr als eine Rolle — es ist die Chance, Luxemburgs Dating-"
"Kultur mitzugestalten."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:112
msgid "Make a Real Difference"
msgstr "Mach einen echten Unterschied"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:113
msgid ""
"You'll be the first person to welcome new members. Your feedback helps them "
"put their best foot forward and find real connections."
msgstr ""
"Du bist die erste Person, die neue Mitglieder willkommen heißt. Dein "
"Feedback hilft ihnen, sich von ihrer besten Seite zu zeigen und echte "
"Verbindungen zu finden."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:117
msgid "Flexible & Remote"
msgstr "Flexibel & Remote"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:118
msgid ""
"Host events when it suits you, and handle quick tasks from anywhere — answer"
" a member's question or review a connection request between meetings."
msgstr ""
"Organisiere Events, wann es dir passt, und erledige kleine Aufgaben von "
"überall — beantworte die Frage eines Mitglieds oder prüfe eine "
"Verbindungsanfrage zwischen Terminen."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:122
msgid "Grow Your Skills"
msgstr "Entwickle deine Fähigkeiten"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:123
msgid ""
"Develop your listening, coaching, and communication skills. Get early access"
" to new features and be part of shaping the platform."
msgstr ""
"Entwickle deine Zuhör-, Coaching- und Kommunikationsfähigkeiten. Erhalte "
"frühen Zugang zu neuen Features und gestalte die Plattform mit."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:131
msgid "What You'll Do"
msgstr "Was du tun wirst"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:132
msgid ""
"A mix of tasks that keep things interesting — no two days are the same."
msgstr ""
"Ein Mix aus Aufgaben, der die Dinge spannend hält — kein Tag ist wie der "
"andere."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:138
msgid "Verify New Members"
msgstr "Neue Mitglieder verifizieren"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:139
msgid ""
"Verify new members in person when they arrive at an event — a quick, "
"friendly face-to-face is all it takes."
msgstr ""
"Verifiziere neue Mitglieder persönlich, wenn sie zu einem Event kommen — ein"
" kurzes, freundliches Treffen reicht."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:145
msgid "Host & Welcome at Events"
msgstr "Events organisieren & begrüßen"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:146
msgid ""
"Welcome members at events, explain how things work, and set a warm, safe "
"tone for everyone."
msgstr ""
"Begrüße Mitglieder bei Events, erkläre, wie alles funktioniert, und sorge "
"für eine warme, sichere Atmosphäre für alle."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:152
msgid "Manage Event Check-ins"
msgstr "Event-Check-ins verwalten"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:153
msgid ""
"Use our QR code system to check attendees in at events quickly and smoothly."
msgstr ""
"Nutze unser QR-Code-System, um Teilnehmer schnell und reibungslos bei Events"
" einzuchecken."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:159
msgid "Facilitate Connections"
msgstr "Verbindungen vermitteln"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:160
msgid ""
"Help mutual matches connect after events. Review connection requests and "
"mediate introductions."
msgstr ""
"Hilf gegenseitigen Matches, sich nach Events zu verbinden. Überprüfe "
"Verbindungsanfragen und vermittle Vorstellungen."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:166
msgid "Guide Member Journeys"
msgstr "Mitglieder-Journeys begleiten"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:167
msgid ""
"Support members through interactive experiences, challenges, and seasonal "
"campaigns."
msgstr ""
"Begleite Mitglieder durch interaktive Erlebnisse, Challenges und saisonale "
"Kampagnen."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:173
msgid "Ongoing Member Support"
msgstr "Laufende Mitgliederbetreuung"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:174
msgid ""
"Answer questions, address concerns, and ensure every member feels welcome "
"and supported."
msgstr ""
"Beantworte Fragen, geh auf Anliegen ein und sorge dafür, dass sich jedes "
"Mitglied willkommen und unterstützt fühlt."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:183
msgid "Who We're Looking For"
msgstr "Wen wir suchen"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:188
msgid "Empathetic and non-judgmental — you enjoy helping people"
msgstr "Empathisch und wertfrei — du hilfst gerne Menschen"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:189
msgid "Multilingual — comfortable in at least 2 of EN, DE, FR"
msgstr "Mehrsprachig — sicher in mindestens 2 von EN, DE, FR"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:190
msgid "Reliable — you follow through on commitments"
msgstr "Zuverlässig — du hältst deine Zusagen ein"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:191
msgid "Connected to Luxembourg — you live in or know the community"
msgstr "Mit Luxemburg verbunden — du lebst dort oder kennst die Community"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:197
msgid ""
"No experience required — we'll train you on everything you need to know."
msgstr ""
"Keine Erfahrung nötig — wir schulen dich in allem, was du wissen musst."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:200
msgid "2-4 hours per week"
msgstr "2-4 Stunden pro Woche"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:201
msgid "Fully remote (events are optional)"
msgstr "Vollständig remote (Events sind optional)"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:202
msgid "Volunteer role with perks"
msgstr "Ehrenamt mit Vorteilen"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:203
msgid "Full onboarding and training provided"
msgstr "Vollständige Einarbeitung und Schulung"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:212
msgid "Ready to Make a Difference?"
msgstr "Bereit, einen Unterschied zu machen?"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:213
msgid "We're all about real human connection and that starts with your voice!"
msgstr ""
"Bei uns dreht sich alles um echte menschliche Verbindung und die beginnt mit"
" deiner Stimme!"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:215
msgid ""
"No hiding behind emails. Pick up the phone, call us, and convince us why "
"you'd make an amazing coach. If you can charm us, imagine what you'll do for"
" our members."
msgstr ""
"Kein Verstecken hinter E-Mails. Greif zum Telefon, ruf uns an und überzeug "
"uns, warum du ein großartiger Coach wärst. Wenn du uns begeistern kannst, "
"stell dir vor, was du für unsere Mitglieder tun wirst."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:224
msgid "We're happy to answer any questions about coaching."
msgstr "Wir beantworten gerne alle Fragen zum Coaching."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:4
msgid "Crush Connect Beta — 4 Weeks, 4 Coach-Picked Matches | Crush.lu"
msgstr ""
"Crush Connect Beta — 4 Wochen, 4 vom Coach ausgewählte Matches | Crush.lu"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:6
msgid "Crush Connect Beta — We're Looking for 20 Testers | Crush.lu"
msgstr "Crush Connect Beta — Wir suchen 20 Testpersonen | Crush.lu"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:7
msgid ""
"Help us co-create Crush Connect: over 4 weeks you receive 4 matches, one "
"hand-picked by a Crush Coach each week. Join the waitlist — we're recruiting"
" 20 testers."
msgstr ""
"Hilf uns, Crush Connect zu entwickeln: In 4 Wochen bekommst du 4 Matches – "
"jede Woche eines, von einem Crush Coach handverlesen. Trag dich in die "
"Warteliste ein – wir suchen 20 Testpersonen."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:9
msgid ""
"Crush Connect is a new Crush.lu concept: 4 weeks, 4 coach-curated matches — "
"one per week. Free for the first month, then €10/month. Join the waitlist."
msgstr ""
"Crush Connect ist ein neues Crush.lu-Konzept: 4 Wochen, 4 vom Coach "
"kuratierte Matches – eines pro Woche. Den ersten Monat gratis, danach 10 "
"€/Monat. Trag dich in die Warteliste ein."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:10
msgid ""
"crush connect, coach-curated matches luxembourg, dating beta, crush.lu, "
"curated matchmaking"
msgstr ""
"crush connect, vom coach kuratierte matches luxemburg, dating beta, "
"crush.lu, kuratiertes matchmaking"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:46
msgid "Beta — 20 testers wanted"
msgstr "Beta – 20 Testpersonen gesucht"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:50
msgid "4 weeks. 4 matches."
msgstr "4 Wochen. 4 Matches."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:53
msgid ""
"We're co-creating a new way to meet on Crush.lu — and we're looking for 20 "
"testers to help. Over 4 weeks you receive 4 matches, each one hand-picked "
"for you by a Crush Coach, one per week."
msgstr ""
"Wir entwickeln eine neue Art, sich auf Crush.lu kennenzulernen – und suchen "
"20 Testpersonen, die mitmachen. In 4 Wochen bekommst du 4 Matches, jedes "
"davon von einem Crush Coach für dich handverlesen, eines pro Woche."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:59
#: templates/crush_lu/dashboard.html:146
#, python-format
msgid "You're #%(pos)s on the waitlist"
msgstr "Du bist Nr. %(pos)s auf der Warteliste"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:63
msgid "Join the Waitlist"
msgstr "Auf die Warteliste setzen"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:69
msgid "Sign Up to Join"
msgstr "Registrieren und mitmachen"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:86
msgid "How the beta works"
msgstr "So funktioniert die Beta"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_connect.html:89
msgid ""
"Four weeks, four coach-curated matches — and your feedback shapes what Crush"
" Connect becomes."
msgstr ""
"Vier Wochen, vier vom Coach kuratierte Matches – und dein Feedback prägt, "
