#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:8
msgid ""
"Luxembourg's dating platform for real connections. Join speed dating events,"
" social mixers, and singles meetups. Verified members, real people in "
"person, no endless swiping."
msgstr ""
"Luxemburgs Dating-Plattform für echte Verbindungen. Komm zu Speed-Dating-"
"Events, Social Mixern und Singletreffen. Verifizierte Mitglieder, echte "
"Menschen persönlich, kein endloses Swipen."

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:11
msgid ""
"Luxembourg's dating platform for real connections. Join speed dating events,"
" social mixers, and singles meetups."
msgstr ""
"Luxemburgs Dating-Plattform für echte Verbindungen. Speed Dating Events, "
"Social Mixer und Singles-Treffen."

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:13
msgid ""
"Crush.lu is Luxembourg's dating platform. Meet singles at speed dating "
"events, social mixers, and themed meetups. Members are verified in person or"
" via LuxID for authentic connections. Join free."
msgstr ""
"Crush.lu ist Luxemburgs Dating-Plattform. Triff Singles bei Speed-Dating-"
"Events, Social Mixern und Themenabenden. Mitglieder werden persönlich oder "
"per LuxID verifiziert — für echte Verbindungen. Kostenlos beitreten."

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:14
msgid ""
"crush.lu, dating luxembourg, speed dating luxembourg, singles events "
"luxembourg, meetup luxembourg, dating events, luxembourg singles, rencontre "
"luxembourg, singles in luxemburg"
msgstr ""
"crush.lu, dating luxemburg, speed dating luxemburg, singles events "
"luxemburg, singletreff luxemburg, dating events, singles luxemburg, "
"partnersuche luxemburg, singles in luxemburg"

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:26
msgid ""
"Privacy-first dating platform for Luxembourg with coach-curated events and "
"meaningful connections."
msgstr ""
"Datenschutz-orientierte Dating-Plattform für Luxemburg mit von Coaches "
"kuratierten Events und bedeutungsvollen Verbindungen."

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:43
msgid "How does Crush.lu work?"
msgstr "Wie funktioniert Crush.lu?"

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:46
msgid ""
"Create your profile, then get verified — come to an event and a coach "
"verifies you in person, or connect your LuxID in seconds. Then join speed "
"dating nights and social meetups to meet real people."
msgstr ""
"Erstelle dein Profil, dann verifiziere dich — komm zu einem Event und ein "
"Coach verifiziert dich persönlich, oder verbinde dein LuxID in Sekunden. "
"Dann nimm an Speed-Dating-Abenden und Social Meetups teil und triff echte "
"Menschen."

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:51
msgid "Is Crush.lu free to join?"
msgstr "Ist Crush.lu kostenlos?"

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:54
msgid ""
"Yes! Creating a profile is free. Some events may have a small registration "
"fee to cover venue costs."
msgstr ""
"Ja! Die Profilerstellung ist kostenlos. Einige Events können eine kleine "
"Anmeldegebühr haben, um die Veranstaltungskosten zu decken."

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:59
msgid "What makes Crush.lu different from other dating apps?"
msgstr "Was macht Crush.lu anders als andere Dating-Apps?"

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:62
msgid ""
"Crush.lu focuses on privacy-first, event-based dating. Members are verified "
"in person at events or via LuxID, and you meet people at organized events "
"instead of endless swiping."
msgstr ""
"Crush.lu setzt auf datenschutzorientiertes, eventbasiertes Dating. "
"Mitglieder werden persönlich bei Events oder per LuxID verifiziert, und du "
"triffst Menschen bei organisierten Events statt endlosem Swipen."

#: templates/crush_lu/home.html:81
