#, python-format
msgid ""
"We do not use any third-party tracking cookies. We do not use Google "
"Analytics. Our server-side monitoring (Application Insights) operates at a "
"5%% sampling rate and does not collect personally identifiable information "
"from your browser."
msgstr ""
